22:29.247 --> 22:31.181
Oh, Carol, honey.

22:33.217 --> 22:36.186
You know, I'm not
very good at quiet talk.

22:36.254 --> 22:39.423
Yelling is my long suit.

22:39.490 --> 22:43.893
I don't know.
I'm trying to say something
and I hope it comes out right.

22:43.962 --> 22:46.229
What I'm trying to say is,

22:46.297 --> 22:48.731
I want you to know that I care.

22:50.501 --> 22:52.735
I know you care.

22:52.803 --> 22:55.839
Thank you, mother.
Oh, honey, listen.

22:55.906 --> 22:57.975
Everything passes in time.

22:58.042 --> 23:00.910
And who knows?
David may still work out.

23:00.979 --> 23:04.681
Even if it doesn't,
it'll work out with
somebody else. Look at us.

23:04.748 --> 23:08.185
It took your mother
four tries before she
was lucky enough to get me.

23:08.252 --> 23:10.487
See why I love that man?

23:10.554 --> 23:12.555
His modesty.

23:12.623 --> 23:17.160
What's going on?
Am I missing something?

23:17.228 --> 23:19.762
Only the wedding, Edith.
It's off.

23:19.830 --> 23:22.932
Oh. I wondered
what she was laughing at.

23:23.001 --> 23:27.837
Geez, I'm glad
somebody's laughing
and having a good time here.

23:27.905 --> 23:29.973
Archie, what are
you doing here?

23:30.041 --> 23:33.510
The same thing I was doing
at the motel, Edith--
not sleeping.

23:33.577 --> 23:36.246
They was having
a wild party over there.
People screaming and yelling.

23:36.314 --> 23:38.482
One crazy dame
was marching to astoria.

23:42.820 --> 23:44.787
Around 11:00
I couldn't take it no more.

23:44.855 --> 23:48.058
I had to call the cops
to come and break it up.

23:53.631 --> 23:55.565
I should've known.

23:55.633 --> 23:59.036
I should've known too, maude.
I never would've went
to the joint.

23:59.103 --> 24:01.038
You fink.
Huh?

24:01.105 --> 24:03.740
If you hadn't
called the cops,
nothing would have happened.

24:03.807 --> 24:05.975
What is she talking about?
If there hadn't
been a raid,

24:06.044 --> 24:07.977
there never would have been
this fight here tonight.

24:08.046 --> 24:10.514
Archie, you have ruined
my daughter's wedding.

24:10.581 --> 24:15.985
Well, then that
makes us even, maudie,
'cause you ruined my weekend.

24:16.054 --> 24:19.222
Ow!

24:19.290 --> 24:21.324
You stepped on my foot.

24:27.998 --> 24:31.034
Maude, I had
a marvelous time.

24:31.102 --> 24:34.571
Carol, I can't tell you
how sorry I am.

24:34.638 --> 24:37.807
Thanks, Edith.
Yeah, Carol,
I was gonna tell you--

24:37.875 --> 24:40.677
Archie, there's
no need to apologize.

24:40.744 --> 24:42.946
All you did was
mess up a party.

24:43.013 --> 24:44.948
I messed up my own wedding.

24:45.015 --> 24:47.951
That's what
I was gonna tell you.
It ain't my fault.

24:50.754 --> 24:52.689
Come on, Edith.
We've got a long trip.

24:52.756 --> 24:54.991
Let's get going.
Bye. Bye.

24:55.059 --> 24:56.993
Keep smiling there, maudie.

24:57.061 --> 25:00.763
Archie. Here.
You don't wanna forget
your wedding present.

25:00.831 --> 25:03.733
Oh, no. I tell you
what you do, maude.

25:03.801 --> 25:07.304
You keep it here on
what you call a deposit
for the next wedding.

